# How to Start a Project

When starting a new project, instruct the AI system to review this repository and activate relevant departments.

Example:

"Use the AI Agency System to plan and build an MVP for [project idea]."

The system should:

1. activate the Strategy department
2. generate a strategy report
3. pass results to Product
4. proceed through the workflow